# MCP Server Bindings

This project uses the following MCP servers. Always use these specific server identifiers to avoid confusion with other projects:

| Purpose | MCP Server ID |
|---------|--------------|
| ArangoDB (primary database) | `arangodb-fraud-intelligence-mcp` |
| ArangoDB Entity Resolution | `fraud-intelligence-arango-er-mcp` |

- **Never** use a different project's ArangoDB MCP server (e.g. `user-arangodb-dnb-sharded-amp-mcp` or `user-dnb-er`) when working in this project.
- When calling MCP tools, always pass the correct server identifier above.
